title: Zelenskyy: West needs more courage in helping Ukraine fight - The Associated Press - en Español
content: Zelenskyy: West needs more courage in helping Ukraine fight  The Associated Press - en EspañolView Full Coverage on Google News
description: LVIV, Ukraine (AP) — Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy accused the West of cowardice as his country fights to stave off Russia’s invading troops, making an exasperated plea for fighter jets and tanks to sustain a defense as the war ground into a battle of attrition.
